description:
I would... err... love to read/see the first two volumes of this series. It's beautiful, and it doesn't need a translation because it's wordless. This volume is about the life of a pride of lions on the African plains. I'm assuming that's what the first two volumes are about as well. Highly recommended for those who enjoy a good wordless comic book (or in this case, a great one).

---------------------------------------------------------

Love - Der Lowe

Ankama, 2012, 87 pages

Written and Illustrated by Frederic Brremaud, Frederico Bertolucci
